RICHMOND COUNCIL SUPPORTS OVER 6,000 RESIDENTS WITH 100% COUNCIL TAX RELIEF
----------------------------------------------------------------------

    Richmond upon Thames has been able to provide 100% Council Tax
    reductions for 6,309 residents, providing a financial lifeline
    for many during the COVID-19 pandemic, Richmond's Full Council
    heard at the annual Budget Meeting on Tuesday night. This
    discretionary support is over and above statutory relief,
    for example to student households.

